{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"","frontmatter":{"title":"Charlotte Lucas","noun":"Experience","verb":"Crafting","intro":"Charlotte is a creative focusing on motion design and digital experiences. A multidisciplinary and passionate storyteller, she sets her ideas in motion through her skills in visual design, data visualization, physical computing, and filmmaking. She believes that as designers, we have the ability to craft the human experience. Whether it is to solve complex problems, inform, or simply elicit delight, she aims to make a positive impact on people through design. When not designing, she is an avid cat-petter, concertgoer, and bubble tea enthusiast.","hobbies":"photography, video games, petting cats, cloudgazing","music":"indie rock, alternative hip-hop, jazz","tools":"Illustrator, Sketch, After Effects, Cinema 4D, Sony A6000","watch":"","typeface":"FF DIN by Albert-Jan Pool","twitter":null,"instagram":"http://instagram.com/char.lc","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/charlotte-lucas/","email":"charlottejazmine@gmail.com","website":"http://charlu.ca/","headshot":{"childImageSharp":{"resolutions":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":60,"height":75,"src":"/the-next-website/static/69bfb2951faa71a8d91d3925cfc659e8/7d7e5/Charlotte_Lucas-1.jpg","srcSet":"/the-next-website/static/69bfb2951faa71a8d91d3925cfc659e8/7d7e5/Charlotte_Lucas-1.jpg 1x,\n/the-next-website/static/69bfb2951faa71a8d91d3925cfc659e8/ab647/Charlotte_Lucas-1.jpg 1.5x,\n/the-next-website/static/69bfb2951faa71a8d91d3925cfc659e8/253d6/Charlotte_Lucas-1.jpg 2x,\n/the-next-website/static/69bfb2951faa71a8d91d3925cfc659e8/55772/Charlotte_Lucas-1.jpg 3x"}}}}},"projects":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"8ad64714-3be3-545e-8171-6254627611f9","fields":{"slug":"/work/code-macro-hackathon-intro/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"code:MACRO Hackathon Intro","category":"Motion Design","image":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":2,"src":"/the-next-website/static/95f4c